mods.abstract: One color window card (blue on white) Hatch poster announcing Little Jackie Shane, Popeye Sommerville and his house rockers at the 400 Club (formerly the Club Revolt) on January 30-31. Poster features metal photoplates of Miss Sandu, Little Jackie Shane, Popeye Sommerville and the Body.
